  <brief_title>Tolerability &amp; Safety of Premarin Vaginal Cream in Indian Postmenopausal Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Postmarketing Surveillance Study Evaluating the Tolerability and Safety of PREMARIN VAGINAL CREAM in Indian Postmenopausal Women</official_title>
